attributes.Long form description: The student starts by unscrewing the top hex socket heads to disassemble the top table of the furniture. Once this is done, the student removes the top table and keeps unscrewing head socket heads to disassemble the first leg. After removing the first leg, he continues unscrewing the second, third, and fourth legs to remove all of them. At the end of the video, the student removes the shelf.
